data.chText: 有趣的；爱嬉戏的；爱玩的
data.enText: full of fun; wanting to play

data.chText: 打趣的；闹着玩的；嬉戏的

before.enText: of a remark, an action, etc.

data.enText: made or done in fun; not serious

data.chText: 他开玩笑地捶了一下她的胳膊。
data.enText: He gave her a playful punch on the arm.

tr: full of fun and high spirits
example: playful children just let loose from school

value.def: A playful gesture or person is friendly or humorous.

example.ex: ...a playful kiss on the tip of his nose.
Her manner is playful and girlish.

value.tran: （姿态或人）嬉戏的，闹着玩的，不当真的

example.tran: 她开玩笑般地把他推开了。

value.def: A playful animal is lively and cheerful.
